{
    "sequences" : [
        {
            "id": "intro",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "intro-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "So, this is where we part ways. I'm sorry I can't help you further.",
                    "nextId": "intro-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "I wouldn't have left the castle if it weren't for you...",
                    "nextId": "intro-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "This is greater than you or I. The people must know the truth.",
                    "nextId": "intro-35"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-35" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Our only hope is for you to reach the rebel camp.",
                    "nextId": "intro-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "You must cross the city and find the rebels in the forest beyond.",
                    "nextId": "intro-45"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-45" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Remember, the city watch is looking for you.",
                    "nextId": "intro-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "intro-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Keep the truth alive!"          
                }
               
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "caught",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "caught-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Here's our traitor. You won't get away as easily this time."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "peasant1",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Are you the tr...",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Do you really need to ask?",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Well, I'm just glad someone is helping out the rebels.",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "The king is skinning us alive! Only last year, they took my son...",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "But you must go, you must leave the city before dawn."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "peasant2",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Traitor! Why the hell do you want to help those filthy rebels?",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "The king cares only about his well being.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "He'd sell your soul to the devil if that could bring him some benefit.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "He even uses the sons of his people as slaves in the northern mines! Look, I can prove it!",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "This is horrifying. My nephew went to the north, they said he had the prospect of a better life.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-6"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-6",
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "I'm sorry..."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "peasant3",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "peasant3-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "You must know the truth, the king is using those who go north as slaves.",
                    "nextId": "peasant3-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant3-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Look, I don't really care...",
                    "nextId": "peasant3-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant3-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "But this is important, please, spread this information, I have proof.",
                    "nextId": "peasant3-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant3-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Well, I will see what I can do."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "rebel",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "We're glad to see you've reached the camp in one piece.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-15"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-15" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "And managed not to bring the city guard on your tail!",
                    "nextId": "rebel-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Not exactly an easy task, you could've sent an escort.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "We helped where we could, didn't you miss the forest patrols?",
                    "nextId": "rebel-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Besides, we couldn't risk direct contact with a possible double agent.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Good to know I'm trusted around here. I even managed to inform the city folk of the king's plots.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-6"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-6" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Well, maybe now they'll send some supplies to help the cause. I wouldn't count on it though.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-7"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-7" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "No royal scheme is terrible enough that they won't forget after a good feast, paid for by the king.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-8"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-8" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Well, I tried... But most importantly, here are the maps and the evidence you needed.",
                    "nextId": "rebel-9"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "rebel-9" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Rebel",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Your effort is much appreciated. This will change the tide of the rebellion."
                }
            ]
        },
